text: The Tilden Park Golf Course is a public golf course in the San Francisco Bay Area. ==Overview== Tilden Park Golf Course is a public golf course located within Tilden Regional Park in the San Francisco Bay Area. It was designed in 1936 and opened the following year == Scorecards == ==References== == External links == * Category:Golf clubs and courses in California Category:Sports venues in Berkeley, California
